ID: text = hida no kic[i] jive ara[bhitu p]rayuhotave
text = no pi c[a] sama[ja] kaṭava
text = ba[hu]ka [hi] dośa sa[maya]spi Devaṇapriy[e] Priadraśi ray[a da]khati
text = [a]sti pi cu ekatia samaye sasu-mate Devanapiasa Priadraśisa raño
text = pura mahana[sas]i [Devana]Pr[i]asa Priadraśisa raño anudivaso bahuni pra[ṇa]-sata-sahasani [arabhi]yis[u] supaṭhay[e]
text = s[o i]dani yada aya dhrama-dipi likhita tada trayo vo praṇa haṃñaṃt[i] majura duv[i] / mrugo so pi mrugo no dhruva[ṃ]
text = eta pi praṇa trayo paca na arabhiśaṃti
